kgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccad683fd97e0f356e68b2b4e5f1d62581faed7","tid":2241353,"uid":105691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:05:26.000Z","msg":"有件事想認真講下，因為未見過區域法院裁決個場面咁核突，所以特登講下。<br />\n<br />\n網上起底嘅陳手足，三項不誠實取用電腦罪、一項披露未經資料使用者同意而取得個人資料罪，罪名成立。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10139\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10139&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbfkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=7b7387a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10139</a><br />\n呢單案審訊時得幾個人旁聽，5隻手指數晒，無一日係滿半個庭，有一日係沒有人旁聽（記唔記得直播台出過呢段文字？）<br />\n裁決當日，10個人旁聽送車（都係同一堆人）<br />\n<br />\n以往係裁判法院陳手足都係得幾個人旁聽，相信有人睇過呢個半年前嘅po，寶寶A就係陳手足（已經投稿者同意可公開）<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/easternhawkeye/13198\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Feasternhawkeye%2F13198&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbfkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=ec103204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/easternhawkeye/13198</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家多寫信俾佢，同埋佢判刑當日，可以滿旁聽席，我知坐滿旁聽席呢個幻想係幾乎無可能實現，不過試下。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/HUVSQ7T6GBBITFVXB2EXXQPNPI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FHUVSQ7T6GBBITFVXB2EXXQPNPI%2F&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbfkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=f7b41128\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FHUVSQ7T6GBBITFVXB2EXXQPNPI%2F&h=8d489f8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/HUVSQ7T6GBBITFVXB2EXXQPNPI/</a><br />\n<br />\n其他和你寫團體<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0%E5%AF%AB%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D-09-26\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2F%25E5%2585%25B6%25E4%25BB%2596%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%25AF%25AB%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D-09-26&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbfkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=4202b70d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegra.ph/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0%E5%AF%AB%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D-09-26</a>"},{"pid":"4b3c1d53f0e81220b08f271abb29df3c27087093","tid":2241353,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:06:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20ce0b655f6c10af5af0f02edee0250e3601841","tid":2241353,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fca6c60a0eba9aeb9243325db580668446cd839","tid":2241353,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcff4f838b14c0dd09bcd86d71d7f9f15a1cd532","tid":2241353,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b397b3cc2af1eff8f90ead125008e2428189f8ed","tid":2241353,"uid":105691,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:56:30.000Z","msg":"我地只要食多d黃店 打Twitter 戰線<br />\n就可以努力返工 安坐家中光復到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets